54.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_chappellroan_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_chappellroan_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_chappellroan_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_chappellroan_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a>昨天（6 月 9 日）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/governors-ball">2024 年州长舞会</a>上展示了一首新歌。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-chapell-roan-interview-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-3582467">Chappell Roan：流行超新星，感觉就像“变装皇后”女孩之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-chapell-roan-interview-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-3582467"><em>NME</em>封面明星</a>在表演期间装扮成纽约出租车，在法拉盛梅多斯可乐娜公园首次亮相了新曲目“Subway”。</p><p>在节目的后期，罗恩也曾打扮成自由女神像，她在介绍“我的怪癖是因果报应”时透露，她拒绝了在白宫参加骄傲活动的邀请。您可以在下面观看这两场表演。</p><p>她说：“这是对白宫邀请我为骄傲表演的回应。我们想要自由、正义和所有人的自由。当你做到这一点时，我就会来。” </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@nme/video/7378761204161858848" data-video-id="7378761204161858848" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@nme" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@nme?refer=embed">@nme</a></p><p>这是 @chappell roan – 涂成像自由女神像一样的绿色，打扮成纽约出租车 – 在 @govballnyc 上首次推出新歌“Subway”。在备受期待的第三天演出中，这位流行歌星还透露，她拒绝了在白宫举行的骄傲表演。 <a title="查佩尔罗恩" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/chappellroan?refer=embed">#ChappellRoan</a> <a title="州长球" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/governorsball?refer=embed">#GovernorsBall</a> <a title="政府球" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/govball?refer=embed">#GovBall</a> <a title="戈夫鲍尔尼克" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/govballnyc?refer=embed